# Description: Tool hoarding on unused boats.
# Scenario: Two boats. Boat 1 executes A1 (requires 5x W1). Total stock is 10x W1. Boat 2 has no tasks.
# Reasoning: The model may allow toolOnBoat[b,t] to be assigned independently of boatUsage[b].
# This means tools could be allocated to an unused boat (boatUsage = 0), potentially blocking availability.
# Expected result: The model should ideally only allocate tools to boats with active tasks, but as currently defined,
# toolOnBoat is not constrained by boatUsage, so tools may still be assigned to unused boats.
# Maximize WorkHours: 10.
data;
set TASKS := A1;
set QUALIS := Tech;
set PEOPLE := P1;
set TOOLS := W1;

param amountBoats := 2;
param maxWorkingHours := 10;

param duration := A1 10;

param hasQuali := P1 Tech 1;
param requiredQualis := A1 Tech 1;
param requiredTools := A1 W1 5;
param stockTools := W1 5;
end;
